      <dt class="news-tit ellipsis" data-level=""><a target="_blank" href="https://finance.sina.com.cn/roll/2019-09-30/doc-iicezueu9257871.shtml">70年看银行业转型：不一样的平安银行</a></dt>
	  
      
      <dd class="new-info">
      <div class="labels col2"><span class="date">新浪财经综合</span> | <span class="time">2019年09月30日 07:00</span></div>
      <div class="oper"><a href="http://comment5.news.sina.com.cn/comment/skin/default.html?channel=cj&newsid=comos-icezueu9257871" target="_blank" class="review col2"><i class="CC-icon-review"></i><span class="num" cmnt_id="cj:comos-icezueu9257871:0" name="cmnt_count"></span></a></div>        
